{"id":122391,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：儿童文学作家中国收入最高/","date":"2010-11-15T08:06:57Z","modified":"2010-11-15T08:06:57Z","title":"简讯：儿童文学作家中国收入最高","content":"<div>\n<p>中国儿童文学作家杨红樱成为中国文学界2010年的首富。</p>\n<p>“2010年度中国作家富豪榜”统计显示她年度版税收入达2500万元。</p>\n<p>80后著名作家郭敬明以2300元收入名列第二。</p>\n<p>另一位儿童文学作家郑渊洁收入1950元位列第三。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/g3fiEeKqZ61dzR_soFpCAlce_r8/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/g3fiEeKqZ61dzR_soFpCAlce_r8/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/g3fiEeKqZ61dzR_soFpCAlce_r8/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/g3fiEeKqZ61dzR_soFpCAlce_r8/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Hj8Rlumyl6A:aF8KviE6nfg:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Hj8Rlumyl6A:aF8KviE6nfg:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Hj8Rlumyl6A:aF8KviE6nfg:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Hj8Rlumyl6A:aF8KviE6nfg:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Hj8Rlumyl6A:aF8KviE6nfg:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=Hj8Rlumyl6A:aF8KviE6nfg:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/Hj8Rlumyl6A\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/11